%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22One%20of%20US%20special%20operators'%20most%20important%20skills%20is%20getting%20lost%20in%20translation%2C%20watchdog%20agency%20warns%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Army%20special%20operations%20soldiers%20foreign%20language%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657f2fa1a79e5746976a5900%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20soldier%20speaks%20to%20role%20players%20during%20an%20exercise%20at%20the%20US%20Army%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%20Special%20Warfare%20Center%20and%20School%20in%20April%202019.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%2FK.%20Kassens%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOne%20of%20the%20main%20tasks%20for%20US%20special-operations%20troops%20is%20training%20and%20working%20with%20foreign%20forces.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELanguage%20skills%20are%20vital%20for%20that%2C%20but%20US%20special-ops%20units%20haven't%20been%20maintaining%20those%20skills.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Pentagon%20should%20improve%20procedures%2C%20training%2C%20and%20accountability%20for%20those%20units%2C%20the%20GAO%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20special%20forces%20%26quot%3Bspecial%26quot%3B%20isn't%20just%20combat%20skills%20or%20superhuman%20endurance.%20For%20units%20such%20as%20the%20US%20Army's%20Special%20Forces%2C%20it's%20the%20ability%20to%20train%20and%20advise%20foreign%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20requires%20to%20ability%20to%20speak%20the%20local%20language%2C%20or%20at%20least%20to%20understand%20enough%20to%20know%20if%20the%20interpreter%20is%20lying.%20Yet%20US%20special%20operations%20forces%20lack%20required%20proficiency%20in%20foreign%20languages%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gao.gov%2Fproducts%2Fgao-24-105849%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20recent%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20General%20Accountability%20Office%2C%20a%20government%20watchdog%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%202018%20and%202022%2C%20%26quot%3Bmost%20Army%20and%20Marine%20Corps%20Special%20Operations%20Forces%20(SOF)%20units%20did%20not%20meet%20foreign%20language%20proficiency%20goals%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%20In%20fact%2C%20%26quot%3Bless%20than%20half%20of%20SOF%20personnel%20completed%20any%20foreign%20language%20training.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%20Special%20Operations%20Command%20and%20Marine%20Special%20Operations%20Command%20told%20GAO%20investigators%20%26quot%3Bthat%20they%20do%20not%20routinely%20assess%20if%20foreign%20languages%20assigned%20to%20SOF%20are%20relevant%20to%20the%20partner%20forces%20and%20local%20population%20they%20communicate%20with%20on%20deployments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Marine%20Raider%20special%20operations%20foreign%20language%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657f2f8fa79e5746976a58f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Marine%20Raider%20talks%20to%20a%20role%20player%20during%20a%20language%20course%20at%20Camp%20Lejeune%20in%20North%20Carolina%20in%20August.%3Cp%3EUS%20Marine%20Corps%2FSgt.%20Evan%20Jones%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EArmy%20SOF%20units%20are%20supposed%20to%20have%2080%25%20of%20their%20personnel%20qualify%20for%20at%20least%20minimum%20proficiency%20in%20a%20language.%20Yet%20between%202018%20and%202022%2C%20only%20three%20of%20eight%20active-duty%20units%20under%20the%20Army's%201st%20Special%20Operations%20Command%20met%20this%20requirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20linguistic%20shortfall%20comes%20as%20the%20Pentagon%20seeks%20to%20improve%20the%20ability%20of%20US%20special%20operators%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-special-operators-focus-on-language-skills-to-counter-china-2022-6%5C%22%3Espeak%20Chinese%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20critical%20languages%2C%20and%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flanguage-ability-is-one-us-special-operations-most-important-skills-2021-8%5C%22%3ECongress%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20demanding%20better%20linguistic%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLanguage%20is%20absolutely%20critical%2C%26quot%3B%20Brig.%20Gen.%20Jonathan%20Braga%2C%20head%20of%20US%20Army%20Special%20Operations%20Command%2C%20told%20lawmakers%20in%202022%2C%20adding%20that%20interoperability%20with%20local%20forces%20requires%20more%20than%20%26quot%3Bjust%20equipment%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20speaking%20the%20local%20tongue%20%26quot%3Balso%20shows%20that%20you%20care.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20less%20than%20diplomatic%20to%20send%20personnel%20who%20speak%20the%20wrong%20language.%20US%20Special%20Operations%20Command%2C%20as%20well%20as%20its%20subordinate%20Army%20and%20Marine%20organizations%2C%20don't%20monitor%20%26quot%3Bthe%20extent%20to%20which%20foreign%20languages%20assigned%20to%20SOF%20service%20members%20are%20relevant%20for%20the%20countries%20to%20which%20SOF%20deploy%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20GAO%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20US%20soldiers%20and%20three%20other%20people%20sit%20on%20chairs%20while%20a%20person%20films%20them.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61143b703dd01000199d3be2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221453%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESoldiers%20speak%20to%20role%20players%20during%20training%20at%20the%20US%20Army%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%20Special%20Warfare%20Center%20and%20School%20in%202021.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%2FK.%20Kassens%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELanguages%20are%20integral%20to%20many%20of%20the%20missions%20that%20US%20special-operations%20forces%20perform.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20US%20Army%20Special%20Forces%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Green%20Berets%20%E2%80%94%20have%20been%20training%20and%20advising%20foreign%20armies%20and%20guerrillas%20since%20the%20early%201960s.%20Language%20proficiency%20facilitates%20this%20cooperation%20in%20a%20way%20that%20conventional%20military%20units%20can't%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArmy%20and%20Marine%20special%20operators%20are%20assigned%20a%20language%20when%20they%20are%20selected%2C%20with%20initial%20language%20training%20comprising%20four%20months%20for%20Marines%20and%20four%20to%20six%20months%20for%20soldiers%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20difficulty%20of%20the%20language.%20(French%2C%20German%2C%20and%20Spanish%20are%20considered%20easier%2C%20and%20Arabic%2C%20Chinese%2C%20and%20Russian%20more%20challenging.)%20Navy%20Special%20Warfare%20Command%20eliminated%20its%20language%20requirement%20in%202021.%20Air%20Force%20Special%20Operations%20Command%20suspended%20its%20language%20requirements%20in%202022%20while%20it%20reassessed%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20language%20teachers%20like%20to%20remind%20students%2C%20practice%20makes%20perfect.%20Army%20and%20Marine%20personnel%20are%20supposed%20to%20maintain%20and%20improve%20their%20designated%20language%20skill%20throughout%20their%20career.%20They%20should%20take%2080%20to%20120%20hours%20of%20refresher%20training%20a%20year.%20Language%20proficiency%20qualifies%20for%20monthly%20bonuses%20of%20%24100%20to%20%24500%2C%20and%20up%20to%20%241%2C000%20for%20knowing%20multiple%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConversely%2C%20personnel%20should%20be%20barred%20from%20deploying%20to%20a%20region%20unless%20they%20speak%20the%20appropriate%20tongue.%20However%2C%20%26quot%3Bnot%20meeting%20minimum%20proficiency%20levels%20has%20had%20limited%20consequences%20on%20service%20members%2C%26quot%3B%20some%20Army%20and%20Marine%20special%20operators%20told%20the%20GAO.%20Personnel%20have%20not%20been%20barred%20from%20deployment%20despite%20not%20mastering%20a%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Army%20Special%20Forces%20Guatemala%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60809c2a4becb800190f6693%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20US%20Army%20Special%20Forces%20soldier%20briefs%20Guatemalan%20special%20operators%20before%20an%20exercise%20in%20March%202020.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%2FSpc.%20Aaron%20Schaeper%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENor%20did%20bonuses%20help.%20Special%20operators%20told%20the%20GAO%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20consequence%20of%20losing%20bonus%20pay%20for%20elementary%20or%20survival%20proficiency%20did%20not%20outweigh%20the%20necessary%20time%20spent%20in%20training%20or%20preparation%20to%20take%20an%20annual%20foreign%20language%20proficiency%20exam%20that%20could%20be%20used%20to%20focus%20on%20training%20other%20mission-critical%20skills.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20problem%20is%20that%20the%20US%20special-operations%20community%20doesn't%20know%20what%20languages%20it%20needs%20to%20learn.%20Theater%20Special%20Operations%20Commands%2C%20which%20oversee%20special-operations%20forces%20in%20different%20regions%2C%20are%20supposed%20to%20advise%20SOCOM%20on%20which%20languages%20should%20be%20taught.%20However%2C%20the%20theater%20commands%20were%20unable%20to%20explain%20or%20document%20to%20GAO%20how%20they%20arrived%20at%20their%20recommendations.%20One%20described%20the%20process%20as%20%26quot%3Bmore%20art%20than%20science.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20none%20of%20this%20should%20be%20a%20surprise.%20While%20many%20people%20around%20the%20world%20speak%20English%2C%20Americans%20(and%20the%20British)%20are%20notorious%20for%20their%20inability%20and%20unwillingness%20to%20speak%20other%20tongues.%20It%20is%20also%20true%20that%20learning%20a%20language%20doesn't%20have%20the%20same%20appeal%20as%20combat%20skills%20such%20as%20marksmanship%20or%20parachuting%20%E2%80%94%20for%20special-ops%20units%2C%20many%20of%20which%20have%20spent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffighting-war-on-terror-took-heavy-toll-special-operators-say-2021-10%5C%22%3Ethe%20past%2020%20years%20on%20the%20front%20lines%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20see%20why%20the%20latter%20receive%20more%20attention%20than%20the%20former.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20if%20you%20can't%20talk%20to%20the%20locals%20and%20they%20can't%20talk%20to%20you%2C%20that's%20a%20recipe%20for%20miscommunication%20or%20worse%2C%20especially%20for%20the%20US%20military%2C%20which%20is%20increasing%20its%20focus%20on%20working%20with%20partners%20and%20allies%20to%20counter%20new%20threats.%20As%20many%20tourists%20learn%20the%20hard%20way%2C%20words%20can%20unintended%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMichael%20Peck%20is%20a%20defense%20writer%20whose%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20Forbes%2C%20Defense%20News%2C%20Foreign%20Policy%20magazine%2C%20and%20other%20publications.%20He%20holds%20a%20master's%20in%20political%20science.%20Follow%20him%20on%20%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2F%40mipeck1%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22a48008f66dd60e4ae3cb2319a8aa10eb%5C%22%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2F%40mipeck1%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETwitter%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20data-xid%3D%5C%22fr1661352660482ifa%5C%22%20data-ml-dynamic-type%3D%5C%22sl%5C%22%20data-ml%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20data-skimlinks-tracking%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20data-am-orig-url%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D031b2d50cbdac0fa31e91243bf4d02324deef0918da59c6d06089ce83c069930%26amp%3Bu%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.linkedin.com%252Fin%252Fmipeck%252F%5C%22%20data-ml-dynamic%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.co