20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20of%20an%20RV%20park%20in%20New%20Mexico.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658c6b9a1c5c7b8c9a0c4ae9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221444%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20view%20of%20an%20RV%20park%20in%20New%20Mexico.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20to%20traveling%20in%20a%20van%2C%20I%20had%20a%20variety%20of%20places%20to%20park%20and%20sleep%20each%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20those%20options%20came%20a%20range%20of%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20I%20could%20find%20a%20campsite%2C%20which%20ranged%20from%20free%20to%20%2430%20a%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could%20also%20search%20for%20businesses%20that%20allowed%20overnight%20parking%20for%20RVs%2C%20cars%2C%20and%20campers.%20Some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freality-van-life-spending-nights-parking-lots-cracker-barrel-walmart-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWalmarts%20and%20Cracker%20Barrels%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20example%2C%20allow%20this%20for%20free.%20Other%20businesses%20charge%20a%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20cheapest%20option%20was%20to%20head%20to%20public%20land%20owned%20by%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Land%20Management%2C%20which%20is%20completely%20free%20for%20campers.%20The%20downside%20was%20that%20this%20land%20wasn't%20always%20available%20or%20close%20to%20the%20major%20cities%20I%20was%20traveling%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20most%20expensive%20option%20was%20RV%20parks.%20The%20parks%20usually%20have%20amenities%20like%20showers%2C%20laundry%2C%20electricity%2C%20Wi-Fi%2C%20and%20places%20to%20dump%20your%20RV's%20tanks.%20But%20with%20those%20amenities%2C%20however%2C%20comes%20a%20higher%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20I%20stayed%20at%20an%20RV%20park%20on%20the%20second%20night%20of%20my%20trip%20where%20I%20paid%20nearly%20%2460%20for%20the%20overnight%20stay%20%E2%80%94%20the%20most%20I%20paid%20for%20a%20single%20night%20of%20rest%20on%20my%20two-week%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20crossed%20through%20states%20and%20considered%20my%20options%2C%20I%20found%20RV%20parks%20charging%20everywhere%20from%20%2440%20a%20night%20to%20%24100%20a%20night.%20Usually%2C%20I%20opted%20for%20something%20cheaper%20like%20a%20campground%2C%20but%20I%20could%20see%20how%20these%20prices%20could%20quickly%20drive%20up%20the%20cost%20of%20what%20seems%20like%20a%20budget-friendly%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt%20was%20convenient%20to%20buy%20food%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20always%20cheap.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20found%20herself%20spending%20more%20money%20than%20usual%20on%20takeout%20during%20her%20two-week%20van%20trip.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658c7817ab6f2ebb11f72bfb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20found%20herself%20spending%20more%20money%20than%20usual%20on%20takeout%20during%20her%20two-week%20van%20trip.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insder%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInside%20my%20van%2C%20I%20had%20a%20small%20kitchen%20with%20a%20two-burner%20propane%20stove%2C%20mini%20fridge%2C%20and%20small%20sink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20just%20enough%20space%20to%20cook%20simple%20meals.%20I%20fried%20up%20eggs%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20made%20pasta%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20limited%20space%20meant%20dishes%20piled%20up%20quickly%20and%20groceries%20were%20hard%20to%20store.%20Between%20the%20exhaustion%20of%20traveling%20and%20my%20desire%20to%20avoid%20cleaning%2C%20I%20turned%20to%20eating%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20cook%20eggs%2C%20I%20headed%20to%20coffee%20shops%20where%20I%20spent%20%2415%20for%20coffee%20and%20a%20breakfast%20sandwich.%20Meanwhile%2C%20eggs%2C%20toast%2C%20and%20coffee%20would%20cost%20a%20fraction%20of%20that%20if%20I%20cooked%20it%20in%20my%20van.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEating%20out%20was%20convenient%2C%20and%20I%20also%20noticed%20I%20was%20spending%20more%20on%20impulse%20purchases.%20For%20example%2C%20as%20I%20made%20frequent%20stops%20at%20gas%20stations%2C%20I'd%20grab%20a%20drink%2C%20candy%20bar%2C%20or%20whatever%20I%20craved%20in%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20two%20weeks%2C%20I%20spent%20a%20little%20more%20than%20%24400%20on%20eating%20out%20%E2%80%94%20more%20than%20I%20would%20in%20my%20everyday%20life%2C%20and%20more%20than%20I%20thought%20I'd%20spend%20while%20living%20in%20an%20RV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20budgeted%20for%20gas%2C%20but%20even%20then%2C%20I%20spent%20more%20than%20I%20planned.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20full%20tank%20of%20gas%20cost%20Business%20Insider's%20reporter%20close%20to%20%24100.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658c76e0ec62ab5daf7f036c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20full%20tank%20of%20gas%20cost%20Business%20Insider's%20reporter%20close%20to%20%24100.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENaturally%2C%20gas%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20things%20I%20budgeted%20for.%20I%20was%20planning%20on%20driving%20through%20six%20different%20states%20and%20covering%20thousands%20of%20miles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20failed%20to%20realize%20just%20how%20much%20gas%20prices%20can%20fluctuate%20and%20just%20how%20much%20driving%20I%20would%20actually%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20while%20I%20had%20mapped%20out%20the%20mileage%20between%20destinations%2C%20I%20failed%20to%20factor%20in%20extra%20miles%20for%20detours%2C%20getting%20lost%2C%20and%20exploring%20destinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOriginally%2C%20I%20expected%20to%20pay%20somewhere%20around%20%24500%20for%20gas%2C%20but%20by%20the%20end%20of%20my%20trip%2C%20the%20final%20cost%20was%20%24170%20more%20than%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20made%20the%20mistake%20of%20not%20budgeting%20for%20showers.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Showers%20at%20Planet%20Fitness.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658c775cab6f2ebb11f72b60%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShowers%20at%20Planet%20Fitness.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20most%20unexpected%20cost%20during%20my%20two-week%20van%20trip%20was%20showering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20my%20van%20lacked%20a%20toilet%20and%20shower%2C%20I%20relied%20on%20RV%20parks%20and%20gyms%20throughout%20the%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20affordable%20gyms%20like%20Planet%20Fitness%20were%20one%20way%20to%20shower%20for%20cheap.%20The%20monthly%20cost%20for%20access%20to%20any%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.planetfitness.com%2Fgyms%2Fsanford-west-fl%2Foffers%3Fgad_source%3D1%26gclid%3DCjwKCAiAs6-sBhBmEiwA1Nl8s18W2xe63YIo7GN7tSkhgf9l5rauuMnalRYK6hToj3enuJ4mJF9JHhoCsJkQAvD_BwE%26gclsrc%3Daw.ds%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPlanet%20Fitness%20gym%20is%20%2425%3C%2Fa%3E%20plus%20an%20annual%20membership%20fee%20of%20%2449.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20I%20snagged%20a%20free%20first-time%20visit%20with%20Planet%20Fitness%2C%20so%20my%20first%20shower%20was%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20then%20planned%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20the%20membership%20since%20I%20initially%20thought%20Planet%20Fitness%20would%20be%20all%20I'd%20need%20for%20my%20trip.%20But%20that%20wasn't%20the%20case%2C%20as%20many%20of%20the%20destinations%20I%20visited%20lacked%20Planet%20Fitness%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20I%20had%20to%20find%20showers%20in%20other%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Joshua%20Tree%2C%20for%20example%2C%20a%2030-minute%20shower%20at%20an%20RV%20park%20cost%20%2410%20while%20a%20shower%20at%20a%20Flying%20J%20Travel%20Center%20was%20nearly%20twice%20that%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20save%20money%2C%20I%20just%20avoided%20showering.%20For%20the%2013-day%20trip%2C%20I%20took%20three%20showers.%20One%20was%20included%20in%20my%20RV%20park%20stay%2C%20the%20second%20was%20my%20free%20Planet%20Fitness%20shower%2C%20and%20the%20third%20was%20the%20%2410%20Joshua%20Tree%20RV%20park%20shower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20embark%20on%20a%20longer%20trip%20or%20if%20I%20do%20van%20life%20full%20time%2C%20I'll%20be%20budgeting%20specifically%20for%20showers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESmall%20costs%20like%20filling%20up%20water%20tanks%20add%20up%20over%20time.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20fills%20up%20her%20water%20tank%20at%20a%20filling%20station.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656a1bf847f9ecb37d8928e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20fills%20up%20her%20water%20tank%20at%20a%20filling%20station.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInside%20my%20little%20van%20was%20a%20seven-gallon%20water%20tank.%20This%20tank%20held%20the%20water%20I%20used%20for%20cooking%2C%20drinking%2C%20brushing%20my%20teeth%2C%20and%20washing%20my%20face%20each%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20my%20trip%2C%20I%20needed%20to%20fill%20the%20water%20tank%20a%20few%20times%2C%20and%20this%20chore%20often%20came%20with%20a%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20I%20paid%20%242%20to%20fill%20up%20my%20tank%20at%20a%20water%20station%20in%20Arizona%20and%20%245%20at%20a%20station%20in%20Utah.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20I%20used%20my%20clean%20water%2C%20I%20had%20to%20dump%20the%20dirty%20water%20I%20used%20to%20wash%20dishes%20or%20my%20face%20that%20filled%20another%20tank.%20That%20meant%20either%20paying%20for%20that%20service%20or%20staying%20at%20RV%20parks%20and%20campgrounds%20with%20a%20dumping%20station%20included%20in%20the%20overnight%20price.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20%247%20for%20freshwater%20might%20not%20seem%20like%20a%20huge%20cost%2C%20it%20could%20easily%20add%20up%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMost%20of%20these%20hidden%20costs%20were%20small%20%E2%80%94%20and%20worth%20it.%20But%20if%20I%20decided%20to%20live%20in%20a%20van%20full%20time%2C%20they'd%20add%20up.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Business%20Insider's%20author%20in%20her%20rental%20van.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657c8bc350edbc52a864cf29%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20author%20in%20her%20rental%20van.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESure%2C%20%245%20here%20and%20there%20isn't%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20could%20easily%20see%20how%20these%20hidden%20costs%20could%20result%20in%20hundreds%20%E2%80%94%20if%20not%20thousands%20%E2%80%93%20of%20dollars%20if%20I%20took%20on%20the%20lifestyle%20full%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20there%20were%20plenty%20of%20hidden%20costs%20I%20didn't%20encounter.%20I've%20heard%20from%20plenty%20of%20other%20nomads%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeople-living-vans-rvs-share-advice-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeople%20living%20in%20the%20vans%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20mechanical%20issues%20can%20rack%20up%20bills%2C%20insuring%20a%20van%20or%20RV%20can%20cost%20more%20than%20insurance%20for%20an%20average%20car%2C%20and%20Wi-Fi%20and%20internet%20plans%20aren't%20cheap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20two%3Cstrong%3E-%3C%2Fstrong%3Eweek%20trip%20uncovered%20plenty%20of%20hidden%20costs%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20the%20costs%20weren't%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESleeping%20in%20national%20parks%20and%20sipping%20coffee%20in%20hole-in-t