hone%20in%20the%20kSafe%20to%20break%20the%20habit.%3Cp%3EErin%20Brains%20and%20James%20Brains%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20think%20of%20your%20favorite%20moments%2C%20you%20probably%20don't%20envision%20a%20time%20when%20you%20were%20staring%20at%20your%20phone.%20Instead%2C%20your%20fondest%20memories%20likely%20involve%20spending%20quality%20time%20with%20loved%20ones.%20If%20your%20New%20Year's%20resolution%20is%20to%20have%20more%20peak%20experiences%20while%20minimizing%20your%20phone%20scrolling%2C%20a%20time-locking%20safe%20will%20be%20a%20great%20investment%20in%20keeping%20you%20present.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20used%20the%20kSafe%20for%20two%20years%20and%20found%20it%20does%20a%20good%20job%20of%20limiting%20my%20mindless%20phone%20use%20so%20that%20I%20can%20pay%20more%20attention%20to%20loved%20ones.%20It%20is%20just%20one%20of%20many%20successful%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fgifts%2Fshark-tank-gifts%5C%22%3Eproducts%20popularized%20by%20Shark%20Tank%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Below%20are%20the%20details%20of%20my%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20catch%20myself%20mindlessly%20scrolling%20on%20my%20phone%2C%20ignoring%20loved%20ones%2C%20and%20getting%20increasingly%20anxious.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221589%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20scrolls%20on%20his%20phone%20while%20making%20a%20face%20of%20mild%20disgust.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62fe8b29f1df7e0018eb2cd9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221192%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESocial%20media%20sometimes%20puts%20me%20in%20a%20foul%20mood.%20The%20kSafe%20helps%20me%20break%20away.%3Cp%3EErin%20Brains%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEnter%20the%20time-locking%20kSafe%20to%20save%20the%20day.%20It%20comes%20in%20three%20sizes%3A%20mini%2C%20medium%2C%20and%20X-large.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221589%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20three%20different%20sizes%20of%20Kitchen%20Safe%20kSafe%20Time%20Locking%20Container%20are%20displayed%20with%20a%20banana%20in%20each.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62fe95e7f1df7e0018eb30ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221191%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bananas%20are%20roughly%20the%20same%20size%20to%20give%20you%20some%20idea%20of%20each%20kSafe%E2%80%99s%20size%3A%20from%20left%2C%20mini%2C%20medium%2C%20and%20X-large.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20sizes%20are%205.5%20inches%20square%20in%20depth%20and%20width%20but%20vary%20in%20height.%20The%20interior%20of%20the%20mini%20container%20is%202%20inches%20high%2C%20the%20medium%20is%205.5%20inches%20high%2C%20and%20the%20extra-large%20is%2010.4%20inches.%20There%20are%20clear%20and%20white%20container%20options%2C%20and%20the%20lids%20come%20in%20several%20colors%2C%20including%20green%2C%20red%2C%20and%20blue.%20Each%20safe%20works%20on%20two%20AA%20batteries%20that%20come%20with%20the%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mini%20was%20too%20small%20to%20hold%20my%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20S10%2B%20phone.%20I%20recommend%20purchasing%20the%20extra-large%20kSafe%20since%20it's%20only%20%2410%20more%20than%20the%20other%20two%20sizes%2C%20and%20can%20also%20fit%20small%20tablets%20and%20gaming%20devices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESimply%20put%20the%20lid%20on%2C%20select%20how%20long%20you%20want%20it%20to%20lock%2C%20and%20press%20the%20dial.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221589%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20screen%20of%20the%20Kitchen%20Safe%20kSafe%20Time%20Locking%20Container%20shows%20a%20time%20of%200%20days%2C%202%20hours%2C%2030%20minutes%2C%20and%200%20seconds.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62fe963cf1df7e0018eb3104%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221191%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20can%20lock%20the%20safe%20for%20up%20to%2010%20days%20at%20a%20time.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lid%20works%20in%20any%20orientation%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20the%20locking%20tabs%20lining%20up%20when%20you%20put%20the%20lid%20on.%20To%20set%20the%20time%2C%20you%20turn%20the%20dial%20on%20the%20lid.%20Once%20you%20have%20the%20time%20you%20want%2C%20press%20the%20dial.%20Then%20you%20have%20a%20five-second%20countdown%20in%20case%20you%20change%20your%20mind.%20If%20you%20don't%20press%20the%20dial%20again%2C%20the%20safe%20will%20lock%2C%20and%20the%20contents%20will%20be%20inaccessible%20until%20the%20time%20is%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhen%20I%20notice%20that%20looking%20at%20my%20phone%20is%20stressing%20me%20out%20or%20distracting%20me%20from%20spending%20quality%20time%20with%20my%20family%2C%20I%20pop%20it%20in%20the%20kSafe.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221589%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20black%20phone%20sits%20at%20an%20angle%20in%20the%20Kitchen%20Safe%20kSafe%20Time%20Locking%20Container.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62fe9686ec781d001868bafd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221191%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20safe%20has%20earned%20a%20spot%20on%20my%20desk%2C%20so%20I%20can%20easily%20lock%20my%20phone%20away%20while%20I%20focus%20on%20work.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20try%20to%20limit%20my%20phone%20use%20after%20work.%20I%20usually%20have%20no%20trouble%20unplugging%2C%20but%20other%20days%2C%20my%20phone%20is%20seemingly%20attached%20to%20my%20hand.%20As%20soon%20as%20I%20recognize%20that%20my%20phone%20is%20monopolizing%20my%20attention%2C%20I%20lock%20it%20up.%20I%20usually%20just%20set%20the%20kSafe%20for%2030%20to%2060%20minutes.%20That's%20enough%20time%20for%20the%20phone-scrolling%20urge%20to%20pass.%20After%20the%20safe%20unlocks%2C%20I%20usually%20leave%20my%20phone%20there%20until%20bedtime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EYou%20can%20put%20objects%20in%20there%20for%20up%20to%2010%20days.%20My%20kid%20put%20their%20lemonade%20stand%20money%20in%20for%205%20days.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221589%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20child%20stares%20at%20the%20cash-filled%20Kitchen%20Safe%20kSafe%20Time%20Locking%20Container.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62fe96cdf1df7e0018eb314e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221191%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhenever%20my%20kid%20has%20money%2C%20they%20want%20to%20spend%20it%20right%20away.%20The%20kSafe%20helped%20them%20resist%20the%20urge%20to%20spend%20it%20quickly.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20recommend%20putting%20objects%20in%20the%20kSafe%20for%20longer%20than%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%20because%20you%20can't%20use%20it%20for%20other%20items%20during%20that%20time.%20Still%2C%20a%20long%20lock-up%20helped%20my%20kid%20reduce%20their%20urge%20to%20spend%20their%20money%20immediately%20after%20making%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20couldn't%20find%20a%20way%20to%20hack%20it.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221589%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screwdriver%20is%20pushed%20between%20the%20lid%20and%20the%20container%20of%20the%20Kitchen%20Safe%20kSafe%20Time%20Locking%20Container%2C%20causing%20the%20container%20to%20crack.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62fe974af1df7e0018eb3177%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221191%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20attempt%20at%20using%20a%20screwdriver%20to%20bust%20into%20the%20kSafe%20only%20made%20me%20look%20foolish.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20a%20variety%20of%20ways%20to%20hack%20the%20kSafe.%20You%20can%20only%20add%20time%20to%20it%2C%20not%20take%20it%20away.%20If%20you%20remove%20the%20batteries%2C%20the%2