20closed%20for%20swimming%20due%20to%20pollution.%20My%20daughter%20and%20husband%20spent%20an%20hour%20or%20so%20by%20the%20reserved%20chairs%20to%20play%20in%20the%20sand%20because%20we%20had%20them%2C%20but%20she%20lost%20interest%20quickly%20without%20the%20option%20to%20swim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20was%20stuck%20in%20the%20room%20while%20our%20baby%20napped%20and%20didn't%20use%20them%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I%20always%20wait%20to%20arrive%20on-site%20to%20make%20certain%20reservations%20based%20on%20weather%20and%20what%20we%20want%20to%20do%20in%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDo%20the%20math%20on%20car%20rentals%20vs.%20transfers.%20Sometimes%20you'll%20be%20surprised%20which%20is%20cheaper.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223294%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20blue%20SUV%20car%20parked%20in%20a%20hotel%20entrance%20with%20the%20trunk%20open%20unloading%20bags.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658c81e7ab6f2ebb11f731be%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222470%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20rental%20car%20being%20parked%20with%20the%20hotel%20valet%20in%20Hawaii.%3Cp%3EEmily%20Hochberg%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20family%20visited%20Hawaii%2C%20we%20booked%20a%20car%20rental%20so%20we'd%20have%20the%20freedom%20to%20explore%20the%20island%20at%20our%20leisure%2C%20and%20transfer%20between%20multiple%20hotels%20on%20our%20own%20time%20without%20worrying%20about%20reinstalling%20car%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20it%20would%20also%20be%20more%20affordable%2C%20but%20I%20failed%20to%20factor%20in%20the%20cost%20of%20hotel%20parking%2C%20and%20that%20my%20child%20would%20just%20want%20to%20stay%20at%20the%20hotel%20to%20play%20and%20swim%2C%20leaving%20our%20rental%20car%20parked%20and%20unused.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I%20always%20consider%20the%20goal%20of%20a%20trip.%20Is%20it%20to%20stay%20on-site%20and%20lounge%20by%20the%20pool%2C%20or%20to%20be%20out%20and%20about%20all%20day%3F%20For%20the%20former%2C%20I%20say%20skip%20the%20rental%20and%20just%20book%20airport%20transfers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20best%20way%20to%20be%20sure%20is%20to%20research%20all%20the%20possible%20costs%20%E2%80%94%20rental%2C%20gas%2C%20and%20parking%20versus%20transfers%20and%20tips%20%E2%80%94%20and%20decide%20which%20one%20will%20likely%20come%20out%20lower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt's%20inevitable%20when%20you%20travel%20that%20problems%20will%20arise.%20Sometimes%2C%20there's%20an%20easy%20fix%20%E2%80%94%20but%20only%20if%20you%20ask.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side%20by%20side%20images%20of%20two%20beds%20as%20seen%20looking%20down%20from%20a%20stairway%2C%20and%20a%20king%20size%20bed%20next%20to%20a%20railing.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658c85fbec62ab5daf7f0c56%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20downstairs%20bedroom%20in%20the%20loft%20suite%20(L)%2C%20upstairs%20loft%20bedroom%20(R).%3Cp%3EEmily%20Hochberg%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20our%20vacation%20to%20Hawaii%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewe%20capped%20the%20trip%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.royal-hawaiian.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Royal%20Hawaiian%20Hotel%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20booked%20a%20junior%20suite%20in%20the%20historic%20wing%20of%20the%20hotel%2C%20a%20two-room%20accommodation%2C%20paying%20extra%20so%20we'd%20have%20a%20separate%20room%20for%20our%20toddler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20arrived%2C%20we%20realized%20that%20her%20room%20had%20no%20air%20conditioning.%20It%20was%20extremely%20hot%20and%20on%20the%20one%20night%20we%20stayed%20in%20the%20suite%2C%20no%20one%20slept.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20morning%2C%20I%20went%20back%20to%20the%20front%20desk%20and%20asked%20for%20a%20new%2