C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703702220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fpaisj408_ranbir-kapoor_625x300_28_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcomplaint-against-ranbir-kapoor-for-hurting-sentiments-in-viral-video-4753993%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20complaint%20was%20filed%20at%20a%20police%20station%20here%20on%20Wednesday%20against%20Bollywood%20actor%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%20and%20his%20family%20members%20for%20allegedly%20hurting%20religious%20sentiments%20over%20a%20viral%20video%20showing%20them%20celebrating%20Christmas.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcomplaint-against-ranbir-kapoor-for-hurting-sentiments-in-viral-video-4753993%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcomplaint-against-ranbir-kapoor-for-hurting-sentiments-in-viral-video-4753993%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcomplaint-against-ranbir-kapoor-for-hurting-sentiments-in-viral-video-4753993%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mamata%20Banerjee%20May%20Skip%20Temple%20Inauguration%2C%20What%20Her%20Party%20Said...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20rare%20instance%20of%20agreement%20with%20the%20Left%20parties%2C%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20skip%20the%20inauguration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022.%20While%20there%20is%20no%20official%20confirmation%20yet%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leaders%20have%20indicated%20that%20Ms%20Banerjee%20does%20not%20want%20to%20help%20the%20BJP%20further%20its%20political%20narrative%20on%20the%20issue%20ahead%20of%2