t%3BA%20wide%20ranging%20and%20useful%20meeting%20with%20FM%20Sergey%20Lavrov%20of%20Russia.%20As%20strategic%20partners%2C%20discussed%20the%20international%20situation%20and%20contemporary%20issues.%20Exchanged%20views%20on%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict%2C%20the%20Gaza%20situation%20%2C%20Afghanistan%20and%20Central%20Asia%2C%20BRICS%2C%20SCO%2C%20G20%20and%20the%20UN.%20Noted%20the%20progress%20in%20our%20economic%20cooperation%2C%20energy%20trade%2C%20connectivity%20efforts%2C%20military-technical%20cooperation%20and%20people%20to%20people%20exchanges.%20Signed%20Protocol%20on%20Consultations%20for%20the%20period%202024-28.%20India-Russia%20relations%20reflect%20geopolitical%20realities%2C%20strategic%20convergence%20and%20mutual%20benefit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20meeting%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20and%20Mr%20Lavrov%20held%20a%20joint%20press%20conference.%20Jaishankar%20appreciated%20the%20India-Russia%20trade%2C%20which%20is%20at%20an%20all-time%20high.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20negotiations%20for%20a%20Free%20Trade%20Agreement%20between%20India%20and%20the%20Eurasian%20Economic%20Union%20will%20resume%20in%20January%20next%20year.The%20Eurasian%20Economic%20Union%20is%20an%20economic%20union%20of%20five%20post-Soviet%20states%20located%20in%20Eurasia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20had%20a%20very%20good%20session%20of%20talks%20and%20today%2C%20what%20really%20came%20out%20was%20India-Russia%20relationship%20remains%20very%20steady%2C%20very%20strong.%20They%20are%20based%20on%20strategic%20convergence%20on%20geopolitical%20interests%20and%20because%20they%20are%20mutually%20beneficial%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20discussing%20political%20cooperation%2C%20with%20regards%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20international%20issues%20including%20international%20organisations%20like%20BRICS%20of%20which%20Russia%20will%20be%20the%20President%2C%20SCO%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20bilateral%20cooperation%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20appreciated%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20India-Russia%20trade%20is%20at%20an%20all-time%20high%20and%20crossed%2050%20billion%20USD%20last%20year.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20important%20is%20that%20this%20trade%20is%20more%20balanced%2C%20sustainable%2C%20and%20provides%20for%20more%20market%20access%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20called%20Russia%20India's%20%26quot%3Bvalued%20and%20time-tested%26quot%3B%20partner.%20He%20said%20India%20and%20Russia%20have%20benefited%20enormously%20from%20the%20relationship%20that%20the%20two%20nations%20share%20and%20added%20that%20the%20developments%20in%20various%20sectors%2C%20including%20trade%2C%20investment%20and%20military%20technical%20cooperation%20showcase%20a%20good%20sense%20of%20importance%20that%20New%20Delhi%20attaches%20to%20its%20ties%20with%20Moscow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20a%20question%20about%20India-Russia%20ties%2C%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20us%2C%20Russia%20is%20a%20very%20valued%20partner.%20It's%20very%20time-tested%20partner.%20It's%20a%20relationship%20from%20which%20both%20India%20and%20Russia%20have%20benefited%20enormously%20and%20my%20presence%20here%20today%20and%20the%20fact%20you%20know%20all%20the%20developments%20that%20I%20have%20pointed%20out%20including%20our%20growing%20trade%2C%20investments%2C%20our%20military%20technical%20cooperation%2C%20our%20connectivity%20projects.%20I%20think%20all%20of%20this%20will%20give%20you%20a%20good%20sense%20of%20the%20importance%20and%20the%20value%20that%20we%20attach%20to%20the%20relationship.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Sergey%20Lavrov%20expressed%20Russia's%20willingness%20to%20support%20India's%20initiative%20to%20produce%20military%20products%20as%20part%20of%20'Made%20In%20India'%20program.%20Lavrov%20said%20he%20and%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20during%20the%20meeting%20took%20a%20number%20of%20steps%20that%20will%20expand%20cooperation%20between%20India%20and%20Russia%2C%20including%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20North-South%20International%20Transport%20Corridor%20as%20well%20as%20establishment%20of%20the%20Chennai%20Vladivostok%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20joint%20press%20conference%2C%20Mr%20Lavrov%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20also%20discussed%20the%20prospects%20of%20military%20and%20technical%20cooperation%2C%20including%20the%20joint%20production%20of%20modern%20weaponry.%20We%20also%20have%20specific%20steps%20in%20the%20area.%20Our%20cooperation%20is%20of%20strategic%20nature%2C%20strengthening%20it%20corresponds%20to%20the%20national%20interests%20of%20states%2C%20the%20interests%20of%20Security%20in%20the%20Eurasian%20continent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20mentioned%20before%2C%20we%20are%20respectful%20of%20the%20aspiration%20of%20our%20Indian%20colleagues%20to%20diversify%20their%20military%20and%20technical%20links.%20We%20also%20understand%20and%20hence%20we%20are%20ready%20to%20support%20their%20initiative%20to%20produce%20military%20products%20as%20part%20of%20the%20'Made%20in%20India'%20program.%20We%20stand%20ready%20to%20cooperate%20in%20this%20area.%20We%20have%20reaffirmed%20our%20aspiration%20to%20strengthen%20energy%20cooperation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Lavrov%20said%20he%20and%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20agreed%20to%20expand%20legal%20framework%20of%20India-Russia%20relations%2C%20in%20particular%20to%20accelerate%20the%20adoption%20of%20the%20agreement%20on%20the%20mutual%20protection%20of%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20we%20have%20taken%20a%20number%20of%20steps%20that%20would%20allow%20us%20to%20expand%20cooperation%20including%20in%20the%20upcoming%20launch%20of%20the%20North-South%20International%20Transport%20Corridor%20as%20well%20as%20establishment%20of%20the%20Chennai%20Vladivostok%20route%20and%2