0Deanna%20Hodgins%2C%20had%20flown%20to%20Las%20Vegas%20in%20August%20to%20celebrate%20their%20anniversary.%20When%20the%20flight%20attendant%20told%20them%20they%20could%20not%20arrange%20a%20wheelchair%2C%20he%20thought%20they%20were%20joking.%20The%20couple%20said%20that%20the%20flight%20attendant%20then%20asked%20them%20if%20they%20could%20get%20to%20the%20front%20of%20the%20plane%20and%20disembark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20said%2C%20'Of%20course%20I%20can't.%20I'm%20in%20a%20wheelchair.%20I%20can't%20walk'%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20told%20Canadian%20media%20outlets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20end%2C%20Mr%20Hodgins%2C%20a%20hardware%20salesman%20from%20British%20Columbia%2C%20was%20forced%20to%20use%20his%20upper%20body%20strength%20and%20drag%20him%20past%2012%20rows%20of%20seats%2C%20while%20his%20wife%20held%20his%20legs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(flight%20attendant)%20said%20it%20to%20me%20a%20second%20time%2C%20so%20that's%20when%20I%20got%20up%20and%20I%20told%20my%20wife%2C%20%E2%80%98Move%20my%20legs%2C'%20and%20I%20dragged%20myself%20to%20the%20front%20of%20the%20plane%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Facebook%20post%2C%20Deanna%20Hodgins%20said%20the%20event%20left%20the%20couple%20devastated.%20''It%20took%20us%20struggling%2C%20in%20front%20of%20a%20dozen%20people%20as%20some%20looked%20away%20and%20others%20looked%20on%20with%20shame%2C%20to%20get%20him%20off%20that%20plane%20%E2%80%A6%20he%20hurt%20his%20legs%20and%20I%20hurt%20my%20back%20%E2%80%93%20emotionally%20a%20lot%20more%20were%20hurt%20%E2%80%A6%20my%20husband's%20human%20rights%20were%20trampled%20on%20and%20Air%20Canada%20won't%20respond%20to%20us%20and%20never%20did%20reach%20out%20as%20they%20promised%2C''%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airline%20said%20that%20they%20apologized%20to%20the%20couple%20after%20the%20incident%20and%20acknowledged%20in%20November%20that%20it%20violated%20Canadian%20disability%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20on%20Friday%2C%20Air%20Canada%20said%20it%20is%20continually%20working%20to%20%26quot%3Bupdate%20our%20processes%2C%20introduce%20new%20measures%20to%20facilitate%20travel%20and%20act%20quickly%20to%20remedy%20any%20identified%20shortfalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''We%20fully%20appreciate%20the%20importance%20of%20making%20sure%20our%20customers%20with%20disabilities%20travel%20without%20encountering%20barriers%20and%20receive%20consistently%20reliable%20service%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703698080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-10%2Fv89umlv8_air-canada_625x300_13_October_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fair-canada-fined-rs-81-lakh-after-disabled-man-forced-to-drag-himself-off-flight-4752889%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20incident%20happened%20on%20August%2030%20when%20Rodney%20Hodgins%2C%20who%20has%20spastic%20cerebral%20palsy%20and%20can't%20move%20his%20legs%2C%20was%20forced%20to%20disembark%20on%20his%20own.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fair-canada-fined-rs-81-lakh-after-disabled-man-forced-to-drag-himself-off-flight-4752889%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fair-canada-fined-rs-81-lakh-after-disabled-man-forced-to-drag-himself-off-flight-4752889%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fair-canada-fined-rs-81-lakh-after-disabled-man-forced-to-drag-himself-off-flight-4752889%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dunki%20drops%20to%20single-digit%20haul%20on%20day%207%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703698029000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106329554%2Cimgsize-20562.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbo