es-unseen-pictures-from-arbaaz-khan-and-shura-khans-wedding-rasha-thadani-poses-with-arhaan-khan%2Farticleshow%2F106328822.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22First%20JN.1%20Covid%20Case%20In%20Delhi%3B%20No%20Need%20To%20Panic%2C%20Says%20Health%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20national%20capital%20reported%20its%20first%20case%20of%20JN.1%20variant%20infection%2C%20Delhi%20Health%20Minister%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20said%20that%20there%20is%20no%20need%20to%20panic%20and%20that%20it%20only%20causes%20mild%20sickness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJN.1%20is%20a%20sub-variant%20of%20Omicron%20and%20is%20a%20mild%20infection.%20This%20is%20the%20one%20spreading%20in%20south%20India.%20There%20is%20no%20need%20to%20panic.%20It%20causes%20mild%20sickness%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bharadwaj%20said%20while%20speaking%20to%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20Delhi%20reported%20the%20first%20case%20of%20JN.1%20variant%20infection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDelhi%20has%20reported%20the%20first%20case%20of%20JN.1%2C%20a%20Sub-Variant%20of%20Omicron.%20Out%20of%20the%203%20samples%20sent%20for%20Genome%20Sequencing%2C%20one%20is%20JN.1%20and%20the%20other%20two%20are%20Omicron%2C%26quot%3B%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20total%20of%20109%20JN.1%20COVID%20variant%20cases%20have%20been%20reported%20in%20the%20country%20as%20of%20December%2026%2C%20Health%20Ministry%20sources%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20rising%20concerns%20over%20the%20emergence%20of%20the%20new%20variant%20of%20the%20coronavirus%2C%20Dr%20Bobby%20Bhalotra%2C%20Vice%20Chairman%20in%20the%20Department%20of%20Chest%20Medicine%2C%20Gangaram%20Hospital%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20new%20variants%20are%20so%20far%20mild%3B%20they%20are%20from%20the%20family%20of%20the%20Omicron%20virus.%20So%2C%20the%20cases%20are%20not%20too%20much%20to%20be%20worried%20about%3B%20there%20is%20no%20panic%20as%20such%20but%20yes%2C%20it%20is%20a%20sign%20that%20it%20has%20come%20back%20again.%20It%20may%20flourish%20because%20it%20is%20more%20infectious%20than%20the%20normal%20COVID%20virus%20so%20we%20have%20to%20start%20taking%20precautions.%20Precaution%20and%20prevention%20are%20better%20than%20cures.%20Take%20precautions%20so%20that%20doesn't%20spread%20for%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20an%20increase%20in%20cases%20of%20respiratory%20illness%20in%20OPD%20of%2020-30%20per%20cent%20due%20to%20weather%20changes%2C%20viral%20illness%20and%20an%20increase%20in%20pollution%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20patients%20who%20already%20have%20Asthma%2C%20interstitial%20lung%20disease%2C%20or%20COPD%20are%20getting%20exacerbations%20mostly%20from%20various%20viruses%2C%20including%20the%20H1N1%20virus%20or%20swine%20flu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20having%20a%20vaccine%20against%20these%20viruses%2C%20especially%20H1N1%2C%20people%20are%20not%20getting%20themselves%20inoculated%20in%20time%2C%20and%20the%20immune%20system%2C%20which%20can%20be%20prevented%20by%20taking%20a%20vaccine%2C%20is%20not%20being%20used%20by%20many%20patients.%20So%2C%20this%20increasing%20exacerbation%20of%20breathing%20problems%20is%20due%20to%20viruses%20and%20more%20because%20of%20pollution.%20Pollution%20in%20our%20city%20is%20very%20high.%20And%20that%20impacts%20the%20lungs%20of%20patients%2C%20especially%20those%20with%20asthma%2C%20bronchitis%2C%20and%20interstitial%20lung%20disease.%20So%20that's%20another%20reason%20why%20the%20number%20of%20patients%20is%20higher%20these%20days%20in%20the%20OPDs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Doctor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organization%20(WHO)%20recently%20classified%20JN.1%20as%20a%20variant%20of%20interest%2C%20distinct%20from%20its%20parent%20lineage%20BA.2.86.%20However%2C%20the%20global%20health%20body%20emphasised%20that%20the%20overall%20risk%20posed%20by%20JN.1%20remains%20low%20based%20on%20current%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703693760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Fs6ih5kqo_delhi-covid-generic-_625x300_23_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-reports-first-case-of-jn-1-covid-variant-4752730%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20the%20national%20capital%20reported%20its%20first%20case%20of%20JN.1%20variant%20infection%2C%20Delhi%20Health%20Minister%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20said%20that%20there%20is%20no%20need%20to%20panic%20and%20that%20it%20only%20causes%20mild%20sickness.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-reports-first-case-of-jn-1-covid-variant-4752730%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-reports-first-case-of-jn-1-covid-variant-4752730%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-reports-first-case-of-jn-1-covid-variant-4752730%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Employees%20Sue%20X%20Over%20Failure%20To%20Pay%20Bonuses%20Amounting%20To%20%245%20Million%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20platform%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20is%20facing%20a%20court%20battle%20after%20staff%20accused%20the%20company%20of%20failing%20to%20pay%20bonuses%20promised%20to%20them%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F12%2F25%2Ftech%2Fx-bonus-lawsuit%2Findex.html%5C%22%3ECNN%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3Ereported.%C2%A0According%20to%20the%20lawsuit%20filed%20in%20the%20San%20Francisco%20federal%20court%2C%20the%20staff%20alleged%20that%20''Twitter%20refused%20to%20pay%20employees%20who%20remained%20employed%20by%20the%20company%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202023%20any%20bonus.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20Friday%2C%C2%A0U.S.%20District%20Court%20Judge%20Vince%20Chhabria%2C%20allowed%20the%20lawsuit%20against%20the%20company%20to%20move%20ahead%20and%20denied%20X's%20motion%20to%20dismiss%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Both%20before%20and%20after%20Musk's%20acquisition%20was%20completed%20in%20October%202022%2C%20Twitter's%20management%20continuously%20promised%20the%20company's%20employees%2C%20including%20the%20plaintiff%2C%20that%20their%20annual%20bonus%20for%202022%20will%20be%20paid%20under%20the%20Bonus%20Plan%2C''%20the%20lawsuit%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20class%20action%20suit%20was%20originally%20filed%20in%20June%20by%20X's%20former%20head%20of%20compensation%20Mark%20Schobinger%20on%20behalf%20of%20himself%20and%20a%20slew%20of%20other%20current%20and%20former%20X%20employees.%C2%A0They%20claimed%20that%20the%20then-Twitter%20management%20had%20verbally%20promised%20employees%20to%20pay%2050%25%20of%20their%202022%20annual%20bonus%20if%20they%20remained%20with%20the%20company%20during%20Elon%20Musk's%20takeover%20in%20October%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fclqkzsemg000k356hsxoz0aj3%40published%5C%22%20data-analytics-observe%3D%5C%22off%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%20data-article-gutter%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E''Twitter's%20offer%20to%20pay%20him%20a%20bonus%20in%20return%20became%20a%20binding%20contract%20under%20California%20law.%20And%20by%20allegedly%20refusing%20to%20pay%20Schobinger%20his%20promised%20bonus%2C%20Twitter%20violated%20that%20contract.''%20US%20District%20Judge%20Vince%20Chhabria%20said%20in%20a%20ruling%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F12%2F24%2Fbusiness%2Ftwitter-x-employee-bonuses-lawsuit.html%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20amount%20in%20dispute%20is%20greater%20than%20%245%20million%2C%20as%20per%20court%20records.%C2%A0The%20annual%20bonuses%20are%20usually%20paid%20out%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%20the%20following%20year%2C%20per%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fzacharyfolk%2F2023%2F12%2F23%2Felon-musks-x-breached-twitter-worker-contracts-by-refusing-bonuses-judge-rules%2F%3Fsh%3D79a75a12146d%5C%22%3EForbes.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3EBut%20the%20employees%20didn't%20receive%20any%20bonuses%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20first%20quarter%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20attempt%20to%20dismiss%20the%20case%2C%20X%20argued%20that%20an%20oral%20promise%20should%20not%20be%20legally%20binding%20and%20proposed%20that%20the%20case%20should%20be%20heard%20in%20Texas.%C2%A0However%2C%20the%20judge%20found%20that%20California%20law%20governed%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr.%20Schobinger's%20lawyer%2C%20Shannon%20Liss-Riordan%2C%20said%20she%20was%20pleased%20with%20the%20judge's%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''The%20court%20denied%20Twitter's%20motion%20to%20dismiss%20our%20claim%20that%20Twitter%20failed%20to%20pay%20promised%20bonuses%20to%20continuing%20employees.%20We%20can%20now%20go%20forward%20with%20the%20case%2C%20which%20Twitter%20was%20trying%20to%20throw%20out%20%E2%80%94%20so%20it's%20not%20yet%20a%20ruling%20on%20the%20merits%2C''%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703692320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fbr0ng3ko_elon-musk_625x300_18_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Femployees-sue-x-over-failure-to-pay-bonuses-amounting-to-more-than-5-million-4753114%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20class%20action%20suit%20was%20originally%20filed%20in%20June%20by%20X's%20former%20head%20of%20compensation%20Mark%20on%20behalf%20of%20himse