es%2C%20as%20well%20as%20an%20order%20that%20the%20companies%20stop%20using%20its%20content%20--%20and%20destroy%20data%20already%20harvested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20is%20a%20major%20investor%20in%20OpenAI%2C%20and%20swiftly%20implemented%20the%20powers%20of%20AI%20to%20its%20own%20products%20after%20the%20release%20of%20ChatGPT%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20models%20that%20power%20ChatGPT%20and%20Microsoft's%20Copilot%20(formerly%20Bing)%20were%20trained%20for%20years%20on%20content%20available%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20under%20the%20assumption%20that%20it%20was%20fair%20to%20be%20used%20without%20need%20for%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20lawsuit%20argued%20that%20the%20unlawful%20use%20of%20the%20Times'%20work%20to%20create%20artificial%20intelligence%20products%20threatened%20its%20ability%20to%20provide%20quality%20journalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20tools%20were%20built%20with%20and%20continue%20to%20use%20independent%20journalism%20and%20content%20that%20is%20only%20available%20because%20we%20and%20our%20peers%20reported%2C%20edited%2C%20and%20fact-checked%20it%20at%20high%20cost%20and%20with%20considerable%20expertise%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Times%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20emerging%20AI%20giants%20are%20facing%20a%20wave%20of%20lawsuits%20over%20their%20use%20of%20internet%20content%20to%20build%20their%20AI%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%20%26quot%3BGame%20of%20Thrones%26quot%3B%20author%20George%20RR%20Martin%20and%20other%20best-selling%20fiction%20writers%20filed%20a%20class-action%20lawsuit%20against%20OpenAI%2C%20accusing%20the%20startup%20of%20violating%20their%20copyrights%20to%20fuel%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUniversal%20and%20other%20music%20publishers%20have%20sued%20artificial%20intelligence%20company%20Anthropic%20in%20a%20US%20court%20for%20using%20copyrighted%20lyrics%20to%20train%20its%20AI%20systems%20and%20in%20generating%20answers%20to%20user%20queries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20lawsuits%20piling%20up%2C%20Microsoft%20and%20AI%20player%20Google%20have%20announced%20they%20would%20provide%20legal%20protection%20for%20customers%20sued%20for%20copyright%20infringement%20over%20content%20generated%20by%20its%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703688960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2F57qtoomc_new-york-times-reuters_625x300_02_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-york-times-sues-openai-microsoft-over-copyright-infringement-4752726%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20New%20York%20Times%20sued%20ChatGPT-maker%20OpenAI%20and%20Microsoft%20in%20a%20US%20court%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20companies'%20powerful%20AI%20models%20used%20millions%20of%20articles%20for%20training%20without%20permission.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-york-times-sues-openai-microsoft-over-copyright-infringement-4752726%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-york-times-sues-openai-microsoft-over-copyright-infringement-4752726%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-york-times-sues-openai-microsoft-over-copyright-infringement-4752726%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hinduja%20Renewables%20bags%20140-MW%20solar%20project%20from%20Gujarat%20Urja%20Vikas%20Nigam%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703688778000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-05%2F25%2Ffull%2F1684992682-9092.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhinduja-renew