ian%20social%20system.%20However%2C%20we%20do%20have%20washerfolk%20of%20both%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim%20backgrounds%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20According%20to%20the%20caste-based%20census%20report%202022%20released%20by%20the%20Bihar%20government%2C%20the%20population%20of%20Hindu%20D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehobis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20state%20is%201%2C096%2C158%20while%20the%20population%20of%20Muslim%20Dhobis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20409%2C796.%20Together%2C%20the%20population%20adds%20to%201%2C505%2C954.%20This%20number%20is%20almost%20double%20the%20total%20population%20of%20Kayasthas%20which%20is%20785%2C771.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20231px)%2085vw%2C%20231px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22231%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%20838w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-210x300.jpg%20210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%20715w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22331%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20having%20a%20bigger%20share%20in%20the%20population%20does%20not%20imply%20power.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20case%20of%20the%20Dhobi%20caste%20group%2C%20we%20find%20that%20despite%20having%20almost%20twice%20the%20population%20of%20Kayasthas%2C%20the%20participation%20of%20this%20caste%20in%20the%20governance%20and%20administration%20of%20Bihar%20is%20minimal.%20A%20lone%20name%20that%20emerges%20when%20you%20think%20of%20Dhobi%20politicians%20is%20Shyam%20Rajak.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20leave%20politics%20aside%20and%20talk%20about%20the%20job%20of%20the%20Dhobi%20caste.%20They%20have%20washed%20and%20ironed%20people%E2%80%99s%20dirty%20clothes.%20They%20have%20maintained%20this%20occupation%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20their%20work%20is%20used%20to%20insult%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20say%20they%20have%20are%20credited%20with%20discovering%20a%20natural%20detergent%20in%20the%20form%20of%20clay%20soil%20found%20in%20village%20fields.%20This%20had%20acidic%20properties.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20how%20a%20large%20population%20got%20involved%20in%20this%20occupation%20is%20not%20known.%20A%20theory%20is%20that%20since%20indigo%20was%20cultivated%20extensively%20in%20Mohenjodaro%2C%20people%20of%20this%20caste%20group%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20perhaps%20plied%20their%20trade%20then.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Brahmin%20people%20comfortably%20wear%20clothes%20washed%20by%20Dhobis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20they%20consider%20the%20members%20of%20this%20caste%20untouchable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20caste%20has%20another%20major%20contribution%20in%20the%20development%20of%20human%20civilisation%20%E2%80%93%20that%20of%20better%20coordination%20between%20men%20and%20women.%20This%20is%20a%20profession%20where%20a%20husband%20works%20alongside%20his%20wife.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20mention%20of%20a%20D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehobi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERamayana%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20A%20Dhobi%20washes%20Ram%20and%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20clothing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20It%20is%20also%20said%20that%20a%20Dhobi%E2%80%99s%20comment%20led%20Ram%20to%20abandon%20a%20pregnant%20Sita.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Brahmin%20class%20of%20the%20south%20connects%20the%20Dhobi%20caste%20with%20one%20of%20their%20mythological%20deities%2C%20Virabhadra.%20According%20to%20their%20belief%2C%20Shankar%20had%20ordered%20Virabhadra%20to%20wash%20the%20clothes%20of%20all%20the%20people%20as%20a%20punishment.%20His%20fault%20was%20that%20he%20had%20burnt%20people%20alive%20in%20the%20sacrificial%20fire%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPrajapati%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDaksh%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20vehicle%20assigned%20to%20Virabhadra%20is%20a%20donkey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehobi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20caste%20group%20is%20known%20by%20various%20names%20in%20different%20states%20%E2%80%93%20Rajak%2C%20Shinde%20and%20Madiwala.%20In%20the%20south%2C%20they%20are%20a%20more%20prosperous%20community%20whose%20job%20is%20not%20restricted%20to%20washing%20clothes.%20There%2C%20they%20own%20agricultural%20fields%20and%20coconut%20orchards.%C2%A0%20In%20Maharashtra%20too%20they%20have%20other%20jobs%20besides%20washing%20clothes%20which%20remains%20their%20primary%20occupation.%20But%20they%20are%20not%20untouchable%20in%20Maharashtra.%20They%20are%20categorised%20as%20a%20backward%20class%2C%20whereas%20in%20Bihar%20they%20are%20categorised%20as%20Scheduled%20Caste.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENeighbouring%20countries%20like%20Nepal%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20also%20have%20similar%20caste%20groups%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20They%20are%20not%20considered%20untouchable%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%20but%20in%20Nepal%2C%20like%20in%20India%2C%20they%20are%20discriminated%20against%20as%20such.%20In%20Pakistan%20and%20Bangladesh%2C%20there%20are%20Muslim%20Dhobis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0and%20just%20like%20India%2C%20they%20are%20treated%20as%20a%20downtrodden%20caste.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20people%20of%20this%20caste%20group%20revere%20Sant%20Baba%20Gadge%20Ji%20Maharaj%20who%20was%20a%20contemporary%20of%20Dr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20and%20brought%20about%20several%20social%20reforms.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%20Read%20the%20Hindi%20original%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F262737%2Fbihar-caste-survey-dhobi-caste-society%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20earlier%20parts%20of%20the%20series%20on%20the%20following%20communities%20by%20clicking%20on%20their%20names%3A%C2%A0%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-ghasi%5C%22%3EGhasi%20%3C%2Fa%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3ESantrash%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3EMadaria%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-koeri-kushwaha%5C%22%3EKoeri%2FKushwaha%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-chaupal%5C%22%3EChaupal%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-nai-hajjaam%5C%22%3ENai%2FHajjaam%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-pasi%5C%22%3EPasi%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-rangrez%5C%22%3ERangrez%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-chamar%5C%22%3EChamar%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fca