%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fd9%2F2023-11%2Fu.s._v._gupta_indictment.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecriminal%20indictment%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20crucial%20details%20are%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edates%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20listed%20in%20that%20document.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20been%20accorded%20a%20state%20visit%20%E2%80%93%20the%20highest%20honour%20that%20the%20Americans%20can%20confer%20on%20a%20foreign%20leader.%20That%20brought%20him%20to%20the%20US%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmodis-us-visit-subject-defence-analysis%5C%22%3Ebetween%20June%2021%20and%2023%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20key%20day%20was%20the%2022nd.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20began%20with%20a%20meeting%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office%20with%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%20Modi%20then%20addressed%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2FSpeeches-Statements.htm%3Fdtl%2F36714%2FAddress_by_Prime_Minister_Shri_Narendra_Modi_to_the_Joint_Session_of_the_US_Congress%5C%22%3Ejoint%20session%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Congress%2C%20and%20that%20evening%20a%20glittering%20state%20dinner%20in%20his%20honour%20was%20held%20at%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhere%20the%20indictment%20speaks%20of%20%E2%80%9Cengagements%E2%80%9D%20between%20%E2%80%9Chigh-level%20US%20and%20Indian%20government%20officials%E2%80%9D%2C%20this%20is%20clearly%20a%20reference%20to%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20state%20visit.%20The%20officials%20in%20India%20whom%20the%20indictment%20states%20were%20allegedly%20guiding%20the%20assassination%20plot%20through%20%E2%80%98Nick%E2%80%99%20at%20first%20urged%20that%20no%20action%20be%20taken%20during%20these%20%E2%80%9Cengagements%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20then%20for%20some%20reason%20that%20instruction%20was%20changed.%20The%20plot%E2%80%99s%20authors%20in%20Delhi%2C%20according%20to%20the%20indictment%2C%20were%20eventually%20prepared%20for%20the%20killing%20to%20take%20place%20during%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20visit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20June%2019%2C%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20%E2%80%93%20the%20alleged%20organiser%20of%20the%20murder%20%E2%80%93%20told%20the%20person%20he%20thought%20was%20a%20hit%20man%20(who%20was%20actually%20a%20US%20government%20agent%20operating%20under%20cover)%20that%20in%20light%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fterrorism-accused-hardeep-singh-nijjar-shot-to-death-in-surrey-bc-gurdwara%5C%22%3Ethe%20killing%20the%20previous%20day%20of%20a%20Sikh%20secessionist%20in%20Canada%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnow%20no%20need%20to%20wait%E2%80%9D%20to%20assassinate%20Pannun%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20June%2020t%2C%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20handlers%20in%20India%20told%20him%20that%20the%20murder%20of%20Pannun%20was%20now%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpriority%E2%80%9D.%20On%20that%20day%2C%20Gupta%20passed%20on%20the%20message%3A%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20got%20the%20go-ahead%20to%20go%20anytime%2C%20even%20today%2C%20tomorrow%2C%20as%20early%20as%20possible%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTomorrow%E2%80%9D%20was%20June%2021%2C%20the%20day%20that%20Modi%20arrived%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fnikhil-gupta-pannun-assassination-plot-documents%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Nick%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20Money%20Courier%20and%20a%20Hitman%3A%20What%20New%20Documents%20Say%20About%20The%20Pannun%20Murder%20Plot%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20June%2022%2C%20the%20day%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20address%20to%20Congress%20and%20the%20state%20dinner%2C%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20contact%20in%20New%20Delhi%20told%20him%20that%20he%20had%20received%20a%20message%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9Cboss%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20that%20if%20the%20hit%20man%20could%20confim%20that%20the%20victim%20was%20at%20home%2C%20%E2%80%9Cit%20will%20be%20a%20go%20ahead%20from%20us%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20astonishing%20that%20this%20assassination%20could%20have%20been%20contemplated%20on%20the%20day%20that%20Modi%20addressed%20the%20US%20Congress%20and%20was%20being%20honoured%20at%20a%20state%20dinner.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20indictment%20alleges%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgo%20ahead%E2%80%9D%20came%20from%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20superiors%20in%20India.%20The%20clear%20implication%20is%20that%20he%20was%20not%20a%20lone%2C%20rogue%20actor.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20indictment%20speaks%20of%20a%20video%20meeting%20allegedly%20linked%20to%20the%20plot%20in%20a%20conference%20room%20in%20New%20Delhi%20with%20%E2%80%9Capproximately%20three%20other%20men%20in%20the%20room%20who%20were%20dressed%20in%20business%20attire%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20clear%20implication%20is%20that%20they%20were%20officials%2C%20possibly%20in%20an%20intelligence%20or%20security%20agency.%20They%20appear%20to%20have%20had%20their%20own%20operatives%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20messages%20to%20Gupta%20%E2%80%93%20noted%20in%20the%20indictment%20%E2%80%93%20indicate%20that%20his%20handlers%20for%20this%20operation%20had%20informants%20on%20the%20ground%20who%20were%20providing%20him%20with%20additional%20information%20on%20the%20intended%20victim.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20indictment%20also%20includes%20taped%20references%20by%20Gupta%20and%20his%20handler%2C%20CC-1%2C%20in%20which%20the%20latter%20refers%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cboss%E2%80%9D%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20title%3D%5C%22Page%2011%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20one%20point%2C%20on%20or%20about%20June%2022%2C%202023%2C%20CC-1%20messaged%20GUPTA%20that%20the%20Victim%20%E2%80%9Cis%20somewhere%20else%2C%E2%80%9D%20that%20%E2%80%9C%5Bh%5De%20is%20not%20at%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20CC-1%20%E2%80%9Cgot%20the%20message%20from%20boss.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boss%E2%80%99s%20identity%20is%20not%20revealed%20in%20the%20indictment.%20We%20do%20not%20know%20if%C2%A0%20the%20Americans%20%E2%80%93%20who%20know%20the%20identity%20of%20CC-1%2C%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20immediate%20contact%20in%20India%C2%A0%20%E2%80%93%20are%20aware%20of%20who%20the%20%E2%80%98boss%E2%80%99%20is.%20But%20the%20evidence%20in%20the%20indictment%20suggests%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cboss%E2%80%9D%20is%20likely%20to%20have%20been%20a%20senior%20official%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20security%20establishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20the%20extremely%20over-centralised%20nature%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20it%20seems%20unlikely%20that%20this%20murder%20plot%20could%20have%20been%20planned%20without%20the%20knowledge%20of%20individuals%20very%20close%20to%20the%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FTaHMOZe_GFw%3Fsi%3DUHrPLZpAuC2l_4LQ%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20could%20create%20excruciating%20problems%20for%20the%20Indian%20authorities.%20They%20may%20need%20to%20consider%20how%20to%20treat%20a%20leading%20figure%20in%20the%20security%20services%2C%20and%20possibly%20even%20a%20senior%20political%20leader%20%E2%80%93%20with%20a%20national%20election%20looming.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20the%20supposed%20importance%20to%20New%20Delhi%20of%20US-Indian%20relations%2C%20it%20is%20remarkable%20that%20a%20murder%20of%20an%20American%20citizen%20on%20US%20soil%20could%20have%20been%20contemplated%20at%20all%20%E2%80%93%20and%20that%2C%20as%20the%20indictment%20alleges%20with%20supporting%20evidence%2C%20other%20victims%20could%20also%20have%20been%20intended.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20fact%20that%20this%20attack%20on%20Pannun%20could%20have%20occurred%20during%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20state%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20borders%20on%20political%20insanity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Biden%20government%20has%20so%20far%20been%20willing%20to%20overlook%20abundant%20evidence%20supplied%20to%20it%20of%20numerous%20startling%20outrages%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20and%20its%20allies%20within%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20include%20attacks%20on%20the%20media%20which%20persuaded%20Reporters%20Without%20Borders%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Frsf-narendra-modi-press-freedom-predators-kim-jongun-imran-khan-vladimir-putin%5C%22%3Eto%20identify%20Modi%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpredator%E2%80%9D%20of%20media%20freedom%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20repressive%20actions%20against%20civil%20society%20which%20even%20targeted%20two%20Nobel%20Peace%20Prize%20winners%3A%20Amnesty%20International%20and%20Mother%20Teresa%E2%80%99s%20Missionaries%20of%20Charity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20apparent%20indifference%20to%20these%20issues%2C%20Indian%20leaders%20appear%2C%20astoundingly%2C%20to%20have%20believed%20that%20they%20could%20also%20get%20away%20with%20a%20murder%20of%20an%20American%20on%20US%20soil.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20were%20mistaken.%20This%20is%20a%20deeply%20serious%20matter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fjames-manor%2F%5C%22%3EJames%20Manor%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20emeritus%20professor%20of%20commonwealth%20studies%20in%20the%20School%20of%20Advanced%20Study%2C%20University%20of%20London.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%